### 🐛 BUG 2 (Edge Case): `toggleShuffle()` Doesn't Persist the Shuffle Change for Queue Restoration

**File:** [PlaybackViewModel.kt](file:///C:/Users/ajaye/AndroidStudioProjects/OfflineMediaPlayer/app/src/main/java/com/local/offlinemediaplayer/viewmodel/PlaybackViewModel.kt#L1566-L1572)

```kotlin
fun toggleShuffle() {
    _player.value?.let {
        val newMode = !it.shuffleModeEnabled
        it.shuffleModeEnabled = newMode
        _isShuffleEnabled.value = newMode
    }
}
```

The `onShuffleModeEnabledChanged` listener at [line 578](file:///C:/Users/ajaye/AndroidStudioProjects/OfflineMediaPlayer/app/src/main/java/com/local/offlinemediaplayer/viewmodel/PlaybackViewModel.kt#L578-L582) does call `persistShuffleMode()`, so this is actually handled. **No fix needed** — the listener correctly persists.

