## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> **Should shuffled playlists/albums loop automatically?** The proposed fix re-shuffles and loops. If you'd prefer shuffled playlists to play all songs exactly once then stop (current behavior, just with the `STATE_ENDED` notification), let me know and I'll skip the `reshuffleAndRestart` approach.

> [!NOTE]
> **Edge case — very small playlists (1-2 songs):** With the proposed fix, a single-song playlist in shuffle mode would keep replaying that one song. This is effectively the same as `REPEAT_MODE_ONE`. This seems acceptable since the user explicitly chose shuffle, but worth mentioning.

